I just thought I'd put that out there.

00:41:41.880 --> 00:41:47.916
It came to me when I was driving around.

00:41:47.916 --> 00:42:02.280
The Lord said, 'You know, if you give this, it would be something else to pray for the people.

00:42:02.280 --> 00:42:08.847
