00:46:19.417 --> 00:46:38.063
Jesus Christ is the same yesterday, today, and forever, and the same Jesus who healed the sick two thousand years ago is still healing the sick today.

00:46:54.640 --> 00:46:55.080
We believe, Father, that You're the healer and the deliverer.

